thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by John Owendoff

author: John Owendoff
title: John Owendoff
text: Had the pleasure to work with the talented staff @ ESS on my recent storage acquisition. They are dedicated, personable and knowledgeable about all aspects of fitting the right storage space to their client's needs. Karen and her colleague (I forgot got her name...Sorry) at the Hazlet, NJ ESS on Rt 36. were very helpful and attentive to my needs. I am very happy with the storage space I'm renting.
